Bstatic.HelpText: Do not link against shared libraries
Bstatic.Name: Bstatic

L.HelpText: Add a directory to the library search path
L.Name: L

_HASH_HASH_HASH.HelpText: Print (but do not run) the commands to run for this compilation

appcontainer.HelpText: Set the appcontainer flag in the executable
appcontainer.Name: appcontainer

delayload_eq.HelpText: DLL to load only on demand
delayload_eq.Name: delayload=

disable_auto_import.HelpText: Don't automatically import data symbols from other DLLs without dllimport
disable_auto_import.Name: disable-auto-import

disable_high_entropy_va.HelpText: Don't set the 'high entropy VA' flag
disable_high_entropy_va.Name: disable-high-entropy-va

disable_runtime_pseudo_reloc.HelpText: Don't do automatic imports that require runtime fixups
disable_runtime_pseudo_reloc.Name: disable-runtime-pseudo-reloc

disable_stdcall_fixup.HelpText: Don't resolve stdcall/fastcall/vectorcall to undecorated symbols
disable_stdcall_fixup.Name: disable-stdcall-fixup

disable_tsaware.HelpText: Don't set the 'Terminal Server aware' flag
disable_tsaware.Name: disable-tsaware

enable_auto_import.HelpText: Automatically import data symbols from other DLLs where needed
enable_auto_import.Name: enable-auto-import

enable_runtime_pseudo_reloc.HelpText: Allow automatic imports that require runtime fixups
enable_runtime_pseudo_reloc.Name: enable-runtime-pseudo-reloc

enable_stdcall_fixup.HelpText: Resolve stdcall/fastcall/vectorcall to undecorated symbols without warnings
enable_stdcall_fixup.Name: enable-stdcall-fixup

export_all_symbols.HelpText: Export all symbols even if a def file or dllexport attributes are used
export_all_symbols.Name: export-all-symbols

l.HelpText: Root name of library to use
l.Name: l

major_os_version_eq.HelpText: Set the OS and subsystem major version
major_os_version_eq.Name: major-os-version=

major_subsystem_version_eq.HelpText: Set the OS and subsystem major version
major_subsystem_version_eq.Name: major-subsystem-version=

minor_os_version_eq.HelpText: Set the OS and subsystem minor version
minor_os_version_eq.Name: minor-os-version=

minor_subsystem_version_eq.HelpText: Set the OS and subsystem minor version
minor_subsystem_version_eq.Name: minor-subsystem-version=

no_fatal_warnings.HelpText: Do not treat warnings as errors (default)
no_fatal_warnings.Name: no-fatal-warnings

no_seh.HelpText: Set the 'no SEH' flag in the executable
no_seh.Name: no-seh

no_whole_archive.HelpText: No longer include all object files for following archives
no_whole_archive.Name: no-whole-archive

nxcompat.HelpText: Set the 'nxcompat' flag in the executable
nxcompat.Name: nxcompat

o.HelpText: Path to file to write output
o.Name: o

pdb_eq.HelpText: Output PDB debug info file, chosen implicitly if the argument is empty
pdb_eq.Name: pdb=

reproduce_eq.HelpText: Write a tar file containing input files and command line options to reproduce link
reproduce_eq.Name: reproduce=

require_defined_eq.HelpText: Force symbol to be added to symbol table as an undefined one
require_defined_eq.Name: require-defined=

stack_eq.HelpText: Set size of the initial stack
stack_eq.Name: stack=

strip_all.HelpText: Omit all symbol information from the output binary
strip_all.Name: strip-all

strip_debug.HelpText: Omit all debug information, but keep symbol information
strip_debug.Name: strip-debug

thinlto_cache_dir_eq.HelpText: Path to ThinLTO cached object file directory
thinlto_cache_dir_eq.Name: thinlto-cache-dir=

undefined_eq.HelpText: Include symbol in the link, if available
undefined_eq.Name: undefined=

version.HelpText: Display the version number and exit
version.Name: version

whole_archive.HelpText: Include all object files for following archives
whole_archive.Name: whole-archive
